interactinfo_80531=團團向思過崖的方向跑了，快點追上<a href="findnpc_new,school07,Event_5nei_wd_55560a" style="HLStype1">它</a>
interactinfo_80532=回答<a href="findnpc_new,school07,npc_5nei_wd_hetao" style="HLStype1">小核桃</a>的問題
